For all designs I ask you to make, have them be beautiful, not cookie cutter. Make webpages that are fully featured and worthy for production. Reference the DESIGN_SYSTEM.MD file when creating pages and visual components.

By default, this template supports JSX syntax with Tailwind CSS classes, React hooks, and Lucide React for icons. Do not install other packages for UI themes, icons, etc unless absolutely necessary or I request them.

Only change relevant code that is needed for the feature or fix.

Use icons from lucide-react for logos.

Use stock photos from unsplash where appropriate.

When creating new features, please add them in the proper /specs folder. Update the roadmap.md file when new features have been added or completed.

Create feature in /specs/[YYYY-MM-DD-feature-name] 
 - plan.md - task groups
 - requirements.md - scope, decisions and context
 - validation.md - how do I know it works and succeeded